    "passives": {
      "IamtheBEASTPassiveABeastRegular": {
        "id": "IamtheBEASTPassiveABeastRegular",
        "found": true,
        "localization": {
          "name": "Belle's Protector",
          "description": "This unit's attacks heal this unit for 100% of total damage dealt.\n\nThis unit cannot be sent to the reinforcements from the battlefield, or be immediately defeated without damage by a non-boss enemy.\n\nThis unit becomes a Guardian and cannot be defeated. These effects begin when this unit enters the battlefield, and end after this unit's third turn on the battlefield. While this unit is a Guardian, for any enemy attack that would hit 1 or 2 other allies, this unit has a 100% chance to redirect 1 hit to itself instead. This unit will not redirect skills that don't deal damage.\n\nThis unit has 30% damage reduction from attacks. While this unit is a Guardian, this unit has 60% damage reduction instead.\n\nIf this unit takes damage from an attack and survives until after the end of the turn, this unit will heal for 25% of max HP and be granted Super Stealth. This healing is increased to 100% of max HP for the first 3 times it triggers after entering the battlefield.\n\nSuper Stealthed units ignore enemy attacks that would damage more than 1 target. Super Stealth will be removed after ignoring 3 enemy attacks since applying, and can be overwritten by other status effects, except normal Stealth. Damage will not remove Super Stealth."
        }
      },
      "StrongHidePassiveABeastRegular": {
        "id": "StrongHidePassiveABeastRegular",
        "found": true,
        "localization": {
          "name": "Morphean Dreamers",
          "description": "This unit cannot fall asleep, or be stunned.\n\nWhenever this unit enters the battlefield from allied reinforcements:\n- All enemies on the battlefield are granted Mega Poison for 200TU.\n- All Earth allies named Belle or \"Beauty & Beast, Pair of Morphean Flowers\" on the battlefield will have their TU reduced to 0, and be Purified (negative status effects like sleep, burn or poison are removed).\n- Then this unit will immediately get the turn by having its TU reduced to 0, and be Purified.\n\nWhen this unit takes damage from an attack, all Earth allies named Belle or \"Beauty & Beast, Pair of Morphean Flowers\" on the battlefield will immediately have their TU reduced to 0. This is not a skin effect.\n\nWhen this unit defeats any number of enemies with an attack while on the battlefield, at the end of the turn:\n- This unit steals Spirit from the enemy team until enemy Spirit reaches 0.\n- All Earth allies named Belle or \"Beauty & Beast, Pair of Morphean Flowers\" on the battlefield will have their TU reduced to 0, and be Purified.\n- Then this unit will immediately get the turn by having its TU reduced to 0, and be Purified.\nEffects that influence TU order may interrupt these extra turns (e.g. Stuns targeting the lowest TU target)."
        }
      },
